headline: CME Group (CME) Valuation Check After a Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Run
summary: CME Group (CME) shares have been grinding higher this year, and the latest move has investors asking whether the exchanges giant still offers value after a strong multi year run. See our latest analysis for CME Group. The latest uptick to a share price of $272.41 caps a strong year to date, with a 17.1% share price return and a robust 3 year total shareholder return of 81.3%, suggesting momentum in CME is still broadly constructive even after recent consolidation.
